'''Nobuhle Mimi Mahlasela''' (yavutse 10 Mata 1982), ni umukinnyi wa filime numumodel  muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]] na model . <ref>https://www.timeslive.co.za/tshisa-live/tshisa-live/2018-02-13-i-felt-i-made-bad-choices-in-my-life--7de-laans-aggie-on-overcoming-doubt/</ref> Azwi cyane mu gukina uruhare rwa Aggie Ngwenya-Meintjies muri serial izwi cyane ''7de Laan'' . <ref>https://www.timeslive.co.za/tshisa-live/tshisa-live/2019-08-22-nobuhle-mahlasela-size-does-not-determine-who-you-are/</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Mahlasela yavutse ku ya 10 Mata 1982 mu bitaro bya Baragwanath i Soweto, muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]]. Mu 1999, yize mu ishuri ryisumbuye rya Waverley Girls i Johannesburg. Hanyuma yize ikinamico muri Pretoria Technikon, ubu ikaba izwi nka Tshwane University of Technology (TUT). <ref>https://afternoonexpress.co.za/guests/-nobuhle-mimi-mahlasela-/2808</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Mbere yo kwinjira muri, yabanje kujya yamamaza kuri ABSA . <ref>https://www.timeslive.co.za/tshisa-live/tshisa-live/2018-03-24-7de-laan-nobuhles-headache-why-am-i-attracting-all-these-young-guys/</ref> Muri 2012, yakinnye bwa mbere muri firime ya ''Mad Buddies'' kandi akina uruhare ruto rwumupolisi wumugore. Muri 2016, yakoze uruhare rwa Nthati muri filime ''Data's War'' . Yakinnye nka Aggie Ngwenya-Meintjies muri filimi izwi cyane ''7de Laan'' kuva mu 2010. <ref>https://www.news24.com/drum/celebs/actress-nobuhle-mimi-mahlasela-has-had-enough-of-cyberbullies-if-you-dont-like-what-i-post-just-unfollow-20200422</ref> Imiterere yamenyekanye cyane, kandi kubwibyo yaje gutumirwa gukina filimi ibihe byinshi mubakinnyi basanzwe.

